OL,7,FROME ` A British holidaymaker with a
OL,8,Fhome in southern Italy has cancelled
OL,9,Fher planned trip because of the
OL,10,F"ridiculous" heat, while a retired UK
OL,11,Fcouple say they are ditching their
OL,12,Fbaking B&B as temperatures soar in
OL,13,FSardinia.
OL,15,FThe holiday island was forecast to
OL,16,Freach 48 degrees Celsius on
OL,17,FWednesday, making it the hottest
OL,18,FItalian region, and a pair of British
OL,19,Fpensioners touring its pristine
OL,20,Fwilderness say they feel trapped in
OL,21,F"a frying pan".
OL,3,CBriton cancels trip to Italy as UK
OL,4,Cpensioners in baking hotel say 'we
OL,5,Cwish we were back home'
